This paper deals with testing properties of distributions, which is a topic that falls under information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of sample access and testing algorithms suggests that this paper could also be categorized under data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
